sun.jvm.hotspot.debugger.win32.coff

Interface WindowsNTSubsystem


  • public interface WindowsNTSubsystem
    Constants enumerating which Windows NT subsystem a given Portable Executable runs in; see OptionalHeaderWindowsSpecificFields.getSubsystem(). (Some of the descriptions are taken directly from Microsoft's documentation and are copyrighted by Microsoft.)

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      static short IMAGE_SUBSYSTEM_EFI_APPLICATION
      Image is an EFI application.
      static short IMAGE_SUBSYSTEM_EFI_BOOT_SERVICE_DRIVER
      Image is an EFI driver that provides boot services.
      static short IMAGE_SUBSYSTEM_EFI_RUNTIME_DRIVER
      Image is an EFI driver that provides runtime services.
      static short IMAGE_SUBSYSTEM_NATIVE
      Used for device drivers and native Windows NT processes.
      static short IMAGE_SUBSYSTEM_POSIX_CUI
      Image runs in the Posix character subsystem.
      static short IMAGE_SUBSYSTEM_UNKNOWN
      Unknown subsystem.
      static short IMAGE_SUBSYSTEM_WINDOWS_CE_GUI
      Image runs on Windows CE.
      static short IMAGE_SUBSYSTEM_WINDOWS_CUI
      Image runs in the Windows character subsystem.
      static short IMAGE_SUBSYSTEM_WINDOWS_GUI
      Image runs in the Windows graphical user interface (GUI) subsystem.
